{"tid":1354600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人做網軍你都可以做網軍","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:20:05.000Z","uid":229459,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de92b8a6213b8a99bfb64d48e425d4429cc85a74","tid":1354600,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以先發制人，去大陸網搗亂<br />\n你係香港同班大陸網軍對駡只係哂緊你自己時間，就算你鬧走咗佢地都唔會有咩大影響，你如果你係喱個時候係大陸網站開佢地波，班專業網軍就要逼住返去回應你，怕你影響到佢地班「平民」<br />\n香港喱邊自然會有人守住，但太過被動對我地嚟講一啲好處都無，直接反擊先係最好嘅防禦<br />\n方法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681270a3d9b27b5d602e0712eaa2d0a60f9c83f8","tid":1354600,"uid":229459,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"香港喱邊就算連仔做嘢都防唔哂班五毛/三毛<br />\n<br />\n你睇下近日佢地幾易帶風向就知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家今晚回POST 嘅時候要加一啲中國禁字落個去，減少冒牌網軍翻牆幫正牌軍手。"},{"pid":"2d2b562ab2a2c9d1a15a63f9c888c9e53aa4d17e","tid":1354600,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c81f730016d31bdef10721cdcfafc7ec3dabb2","tid":1354600,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05e58e648f9c51a8803df585472056ff1305c09","tid":1354600,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d5467ef831e11f21f939da40c3644953aeda54","tid":1354600,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86913860325d53ffd81550342c02265d96e10184","tid":1354600,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":